:"2019-07-27T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"了結唔到兼死左無人知。算把啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c324c7cfffdeb37a09416c3f4147ad61576c7775","tid":1371171,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"年年咁多人上訪 都對唔到北京 你？"},{"pid":"762bb28eb61f86f4d12d9d04a01c6c5bb5aa40ec","tid":1371171,"uid":77761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"唔好死住，留返條命仔咬返你仇人"},{"pid":"f83edab6c513c90a9c1fe2d77fee724421dd6020","tid":1371171,"uid":37111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"唔好死<br />\n認真<br />\n你比你想像中有用得多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個都不能少</span>呀"},{"pid":"15121a8d117b51cbb5235181280cb46560aa5f46","tid":1371171,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39bc46210710e1dcdcd44a416e4dd821615be920","tid":1371171,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"好唔開心好想死 我想去北京了結咗共產黨算<br />\n希望會幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事，因為我也是身在香港的一份子。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存太多，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你的控制。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT1x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=739487b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一<br />\n時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"9c387bf09d15ba66cd7a55333328332ddae61a46","tid":1371171,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"每次出黎流水社運 可能會有驚喜呢"},{"pid":"8879e3a1b5df12a63725d943a9bbb77085e308b7","tid":1371171,"uid":281720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"老實講，雜種可能都只係個傀儡，有無諗過？<br />\n<br />\n要消滅共狗，估計要令一大班人消失先得。。。<br />\n<br />\n難怪金正恩要玩核武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53503977d1a0a03b0c97612392011c47fefd3b0c","tid":1371171,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"鬥長命慢慢同佢玩呀師兄，一時三刻搞唔死佢，齊上齊落共同進退"},{"pid":"99e1f32fc3cd2b4c538feb6ade59e33e4ef7fdb8","tid":1371171,"uid":41853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"你連天安門門口賣飛個呀姐都打唔贏，仲話了結共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e64322611eea14621fe8dea2073e463813e2a7","tid":1371171,"uid":8812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"媽媽呢"},{"pid":"0d921142c71f469fb419c72a927b429736a2f970","tid":1371171,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"毅進警察 社會垃圾<br />\n畜蟲小隊 冚家富貴"},{"pid":"65fbd2d5daa36b6a0251f1056b4281d88aadf646","tid":1371171,"uid":96196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"梁天琦等緊大家，一個都不能小。"},{"pid":"89de252f0c0cbba1a408ac291f9cfc1c4ef64612","tid":1371171,"uid":263712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:28:40.000Z","msg":"依位巴打唔好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8964都無死過人<br />\n你去北京都係無人知你死<br />\n所以留返條命